#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.26"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.26:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.26:0.2"
msgid "3. Uruvelavagga"
msgstr "3. At Uruvelā"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: kuhakasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.26:0.3"
msgid "26. Kuhasutta"
msgstr "26. Deceivers"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.26:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Ye te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū kuhā thaddhā lapā siṅgī unnaḷā asamāhitā, na me "
"te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū māmakā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, those mendicants who are deceivers, stubborn, flatterers, "
"frauds, insolent, and scattered: they are no mendicants of mine."

msgctxt "an4.26:1.2"
msgid ""
"Apagatā ca te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū imasmā dhammavinayā, na ca te imasmiṃ "
"dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ viruḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjanti."
msgstr ""
"They’ve left this teaching and training, and they don’t achieve growth, "
"improvement, or maturity in this teaching and training."

msgctxt "an4.26:1.3"
msgid ""
"Ye ca kho te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū nikkuhā nillapā dhīrā atthaddhā susamāhitā, "
"te kho me, bhikkhave, bhikkhū māmakā."
msgstr ""
"But those mendicants who are genuine, not flatterers, wise, amenable, and "
"serene: they are mendicants of mine."

msgctxt "an4.26:1.4"
msgid "Anapagatā ca te, bhikkhave, bhikkhū imasmā dhammavinayā."
msgstr "They haven’t left this teaching and training,"

msgctxt "an4.26:1.5"
msgid "Te ca imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ viruḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjantīti."
msgstr ""
"and they achieve growth, improvement, or maturity in this teaching and "
"training."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.26:2.1"
msgid "Kuhā thaddhā lapā siṅgī,"
msgstr "Those who are deceivers, stubborn, flatterers, and frauds,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.26:2.2"
msgid "unnaḷā asamāhitā;"
msgstr "insolent and scattered:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.26:2.3"
msgid "Na te dhamme virūhanti,"
msgstr "these don’t grow in the teaching"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.26:2.4"
msgid "sammāsambuddhadesite."
msgstr "that was taught by the perfected Buddha."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.26:3.1"
msgid "Nikkuhā nillapā dhīrā,"
msgstr "But those who are genuine, not flatterers, wise,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.26:3.2"
msgid "atthaddhā susamāhitā;"
msgstr "amenable, and serene:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.26:3.3"
msgid "Te ve dhamme virūhanti,"
msgstr "these do grow in the teaching"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.26:3.4"
msgid "sammāsambuddhadesite”ti."
msgstr "that was taught by the perfected Buddha.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.26:3.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
